desc: WRAPTIE’s tie down straps are the perfect multifunctional strap for your everyday needs. Made from sturdy, industrial-grade webbing materials, these all-purpose straps replace rope, bungee cords, and even ratchet straps. Secure heavy objects or bundle large and small loads alike — WRAPTIE does it all!
